**\\n- 数据传输加密\\n- 访问控制和认证\\n- 敏感数据脱敏\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**5. 成本效率（Cost Efficiency）**\\n- 资源利用率优化\\n- 按需付费模型\\n- 成本监控和预警\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-200\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-blue-900 font-medium\",\"children\":[\"💡 \",\"生产系统需要关注可靠性、可扩展性、可观测性、安全性和成本效率。\"]}]}]]}]\n4:[\"$\",\"div\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":3}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"AI应用的部署架构\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**典型架构**：\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"```\\n用户 → CDN → 负载均衡 → API网关 → 应用服务 → 模型推理\\n                                      ↓\\n                                   向量数据库\\n                                      ↓\\n                                   缓存层(Redis)\\n```\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**关键组件**：\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**API网关**：\\n- 认证授权\\n- 限流熔断\\n- 请求路由\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**应用服务**：\\n- 无状态设计\\n- 容器化部署（Docker/K8s）\\n- 水平扩展\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**模型推理**：\\n- 模型服务化（如vLLM）\\n- 批处理优化\\n- GPU资源管理\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**数据层**：\\n- 向量数据库集群\\n- 主从复制\\n- 定期备份\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n5:[\"$\",\"div\",\"3\",{\"cl